  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you can draw on the mystical power of night to rise into the air. As a <strong>bonus action</strong> when you are in dim light or darkness, you can magically give yourself a flying speed equal to your walking speed for <strong>1 minute</strong>. You can use this bonus action a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
